WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:07.090
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:07.090 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 22]

00:01:15.830 --> 00:01:16.810
You have to shoulder the responsibility.

00:01:19.470 --> 00:01:20.420
You don't have the right to give up.

00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:22.370
And you can't throw your life away.

00:01:27.030 --> 00:01:28.290
You have to live on

00:01:28.550 --> 00:01:31.450
For Yue for thousands of years.

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:33.250
Tongzhou,

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:37.450
I'll leave Yue and Jingwu to you.

00:01:45.800 --> 00:01:46.730
You're right.

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:50.060
I am Prince Ying of the Yue State.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.700
I will rescue Jingwu

00:01:55.160 --> 00:01:56.450
And

00:01:58.030 --> 00:01:59.530
All my people.

00:02:00.830 --> 00:02:05.170
I'll never let Tonghe and uncle

00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:08.780
Down again.

00:02:18.900 --> 00:02:19.850
Heaven's justice prevails.

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:22.180
We'll avenge all those

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:22.970
Who died unjustly.

00:03:28.550 --> 00:03:29.780
That old fool

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:32.530
Even infused Burning Flame into his spirit energy

00:03:32.870 --> 00:03:35.460
At death's door to ambush me.

00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:51.620
They are mostly tied to the Divine Tree.

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.020
Whoever gains the Divine Tree

00:03:54.320 --> 00:03:57.530
Will reign supreme under heaven.

00:04:00.360 --> 00:04:01.060
Who's there?

00:04:01.480 --> 00:04:02.130
Father.

00:04:09.710 --> 00:04:10.250
Father.

00:04:15.430 --> 00:04:16.740
What brings you here?

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:21.370
I'm worried about your injuries,

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.010
So I decocted medicinal herbs

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:25.500
To purge your poison and restore your strength.

00:04:26.710 --> 00:04:28.740
My injuries are trivial.

00:04:29.390 --> 00:04:31.450
A few days' meditation will heal me.

00:04:33.350 --> 00:04:33.890
Understood.

00:04:36.470 --> 00:04:38.370
Have you found Ji Tongzhou?

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:40.180
Not yet.

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.100
But I know him well.

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:44.980
He will never leave Duantu.

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:46.130
Rest assured.

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.810
I'll capture him by any means.

00:04:50.080 --> 00:04:51.210
Can you bring yourself to do it?

00:04:53.270 --> 00:04:56.210
I cannot. I love him so deeply,

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:58.420
Yet he never sees me.

00:04:59.320 --> 00:05:00.130
I will not accept this.

00:05:00.700 --> 00:05:02.130
I must subdue him

00:05:02.710 --> 00:05:04.100
And make him mine alone.

00:05:06.390 --> 00:05:07.810
You promised me once

00:05:08.580 --> 00:05:09.770
You would spare his life.

00:05:10.270 --> 00:05:11.890
I'll keep my word.

00:05:12.710 --> 00:05:13.250
Also,

00:05:13.910 --> 00:05:16.010
Seize Jiang Lifei and Lei Xiuyuan

00:05:16.030 --> 00:05:17.060
And bring them to me.

00:05:19.340 --> 00:05:22.250
You want to seek the Divine Tree from...

00:05:23.900 --> 00:05:25.890
Yes. I see.

00:05:26.660 --> 00:05:30.890
Now prepare yourself to be the Empress of the Yue State.

00:05:51.790 --> 00:05:52.890
Lanya set up a mourning hall at the palace gate

00:05:53.460 --> 00:05:54.810
And held Crown Prince Ji Jingwu hostage

00:05:55.020 --> 00:05:55.980
To force the Yue people to surrender.

00:05:59.580 --> 00:06:00.330
I'll scout for news.

00:06:00.830 --> 00:06:01.570
Look after Tongzhou.

00:06:03.980 --> 00:06:04.570
Wait.

00:06:07.460 --> 00:06:08.420
I'm coming with you.

00:06:08.910 --> 00:06:09.420
But...

00:06:09.460 --> 00:06:09.940
Lifei.

00:06:14.220 --> 00:06:16.100
We'll set off together later tonight.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:34.760
[Mingkun Gate]

00:06:50.710 --> 00:06:52.100
Zhijie, wake up.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:53.330
It's Mingli.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:54.450
Halt!

00:07:26.710 --> 00:07:27.540
Guard your heart meridians!

00:07:44.390 --> 00:07:45.450
Zhijie, let's go now.

00:07:45.910 --> 00:07:46.660
Mingli, go on ahead.

00:07:47.350 --> 00:07:48.300
I'll catch up to you.

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:14.210
The crown prince is an imposter! Escort the Yue Emperor away!

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:22.420
Zhijie,

00:08:23.590 --> 00:08:24.300
You know

00:08:25.150 --> 00:08:26.300
I had no choice.

00:08:26.640 --> 00:08:27.370
I never wanted this.

00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:29.540
We grew up side by side.

00:08:30.590 --> 00:08:32.420
You won't harm me, will you?

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:38.940
Your Ladyship,

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:47.180
Stop while you still can.

00:09:08.830 --> 00:09:09.970
Your Ladyship.

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:12.660
Your...

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:20.610
After them!

00:09:27.350 --> 00:09:28.060
Search over there.

00:09:28.710 --> 00:09:29.570
Check thoroughly.

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:33.610
Head that way.

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:34.420
All right.

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:35.450
Nothing here.

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:36.610
Nothing here.

00:09:37.110 --> 00:09:37.570
Search every corner!

00:09:50.470 --> 00:09:51.380
We're surrounded by pursuers.

00:09:51.990 --> 00:09:52.420
What do we do?

00:09:52.750 --> 00:09:53.850
They're after me.

00:09:54.590 --> 00:09:55.330
I'll lead them away.

00:09:55.510 --> 00:09:55.940
No way.

00:09:56.350 --> 00:09:57.380
Your Highness, don't risk yourself.

00:09:58.750 --> 00:09:59.570
Leave with the Yue Emperor.

00:10:00.040 --> 00:10:01.330
Tongzhou and I will draw them off.

00:10:01.830 --> 00:10:02.330
Count me in.

00:10:11.870 --> 00:10:12.450
Tongzhou.

00:10:16.590 --> 00:10:17.210
Tongzhou. Tongzhou.

00:10:17.800 --> 00:10:19.660
Tongzhou.

00:10:19.870 --> 00:10:20.260
Keep up!

00:10:32.750 --> 00:10:34.060
Miss, please.

00:10:34.230 --> 00:10:35.180
Spare some food for me.

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:43.330
Hurry.

00:10:48.470 --> 00:10:48.970
Follow me.

00:10:51.660 --> 00:10:51.970
Let's go.

00:11:11.990 --> 00:11:13.450
Rest easy, you're safe here.

00:11:21.400 --> 00:11:22.730
You might show your true face,

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.690
So we may repay you later.

00:11:27.110 --> 00:11:28.490
Uncle!

00:11:30.630 --> 00:11:31.420
Jingwu.

00:11:33.160 --> 00:11:33.660
Jingwu.

00:11:35.230 --> 00:11:35.690
Jingwu!

00:11:36.050 --> 00:11:37.200
[Ji Jingwu]

00:11:37.750 --> 00:11:39.380
He's the real Crown Prince.

00:11:42.040 --> 00:11:42.940
Then who are you?

00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:47.690
I'm Miaoqing, a palace maid

00:11:48.660 --> 00:11:49.300
Serving His Highness.

00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:54.850
You're no maid.

00:11:55.660 --> 00:11:56.940
You're a dancer from Yange Hall.

00:11:57.750 --> 00:11:59.060
You used Jingwu to get close to us.

00:11:59.350 --> 00:12:00.300
What do you want?

00:12:01.350 --> 00:12:01.810
Speak!

00:12:03.230 --> 00:12:04.850
Uncle, let her go!

00:12:05.470 --> 00:12:06.810
She's telling the truth.

00:12:11.280 --> 00:12:12.380
She saved us twice.

00:12:12.830 --> 00:12:13.850
She means no harm.

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:14.810
Let's hear her out first.

00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:24.420
Your Highness still remembers me.

00:12:24.960 --> 00:12:26.730
I'm indeed a dancer from Yange Hall.

00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:29.090
I've long been grateful for you saving my life.

00:12:29.540 --> 00:12:30.420
Later, Match...

00:12:34.160 --> 00:12:35.490
Guided by a master,

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:36.810
I came to Yue State

00:12:37.280 --> 00:12:38.140
And sneaked into the palace,

00:12:38.660 --> 00:12:42.140
Thinking I could repay your kindness.

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:48.210
Where did you get this spirit talisman?

00:12:48.870 --> 00:12:51.490
Perhaps from that master.

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:54.020
Shortly after he sent me here,

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:56.140
I found it in my robes.

00:12:56.280 --> 00:12:58.300
I believe he foresaw my peril

00:12:58.830 --> 00:12:59.570
And left it for my protection.

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.850
Could it be the Matchmaker at Lugong Town?

00:13:05.590 --> 00:13:06.690
I do not know,

00:13:07.280 --> 00:13:10.140
But I did meet him under the Matchmaker Tree.

00:13:10.990 --> 00:13:11.490
Uncle,

00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:14.140
If not for Miaoqing,

00:13:14.350 --> 00:13:17.780
I would've been captured by Lanya.

00:13:18.750 --> 00:13:21.180
Your Highness, when Dauntu fell under siege,

00:13:21.660 --> 00:13:23.140
His Majesty bade me safeguard

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:24.450
The Crown Prince at all costs.

00:13:26.830 --> 00:13:27.690
The palace is in utter chaos.

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:29.330
You must protect Jingwu.

00:13:31.590 --> 00:13:32.300
Understood.

00:13:46.200 --> 00:13:46.730
What are you doing?

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:51.450
My stomach hurts terribly.

00:13:53.350 --> 00:13:55.660
Your Ladyship, I shall take His Highness to relieve himself.

00:13:57.510 --> 00:13:58.570
Bring him back soon.

00:13:59.540 --> 00:14:00.090
Understood.

00:14:16.040 --> 00:14:17.260
Now that Lanya has lost her hostage,

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:19.540
No wonder she schemed with a fake prince.

00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:24.210
You're sharp-witted.

00:14:24.800 --> 00:14:25.810
Knowing Duantu was dangerous,

00:14:26.510 --> 00:14:27.490
Why did you not flee?

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:30.260
First, the city gates were heavily guarded.

00:14:30.590 --> 00:14:31.570
I dared not risk it.

00:14:32.710 --> 00:14:33.330
Second,

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:37.140
I trusted Your Highness would come to our rescue.

00:14:37.800 --> 00:14:40.020
Thus, I hid here with Jingwu,

00:14:40.400 --> 00:14:41.490
Waiting for Your Highness's return.

00:14:44.350 --> 00:14:45.690
Uncle, you're back.

00:14:45.710 --> 00:14:47.940
Can we rescue my father?

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.420
It's my fault for failing you.

00:14:56.510 --> 00:14:57.850
I'll spare no effort

00:14:58.630 --> 00:14:59.490
To defend the Yue State

00:15:00.990 --> 00:15:02.180
And never let your father down again.

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:39.090
Still no breakthrough.

00:15:39.800 --> 00:15:41.610
Why can't I break through the third level?

00:15:50.040 --> 00:15:51.570
Weighed down by mortal attachments,

00:15:51.990 --> 00:15:53.730
You cannot cut off all affection and desire.

00:15:54.320 --> 00:15:56.090
The third level is incredibly hard to break through.

00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:58.780
Only with heavenly and earthly treasures

00:15:58.800 --> 00:16:00.300
And purest spirit energy

00:16:00.510 --> 00:16:03.140
Might you stand a slim chance.

00:16:08.990 --> 00:16:10.380
Purest spirit energy?

00:16:36.320 --> 00:16:37.490
Why would you take your own life?

00:16:37.960 --> 00:16:39.180
I had no thought of dying.

00:16:40.080 --> 00:16:42.450
I want to return to the palace, slay the villains,

00:16:42.920 --> 00:16:43.810
And avenge His Majesty.

00:16:45.040 --> 00:16:46.730
The palace is swarming with Longming Sanctuary's disciples.

00:16:47.590 --> 00:16:49.900
What can a frail girl like you accomplish?

00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:51.690
I grew up by the water

00:16:51.920 --> 00:16:52.810
And excel at swimming.

00:16:53.440 --> 00:16:54.690
Before I left Lugong Town,

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:57.380
Mr. Yan gave me immortal cultivation manuals.

00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:58.570
I know a few spirit arts

00:16:58.710 --> 00:16:59.450
To protect myself.

00:17:00.510 --> 00:17:02.380
I'm just nobody.

00:17:02.830 --> 00:17:04.900
At worst, I'll take them down with me.

00:17:05.320 --> 00:17:06.610
I can still be of some use.

00:17:09.990 --> 00:17:11.580
I only saved you on a whim once.

00:17:12.310 --> 00:17:13.450
No need to sacrifice yourself.

00:17:15.270 --> 00:17:16.660
I've endured hardship since childhood.

00:17:17.550 --> 00:17:19.180
Though I entered Yange Hall,

00:17:19.880 --> 00:17:22.290
I was merely an ant, unnoticed by all.

00:17:22.840 --> 00:17:23.970
Only that day,

00:17:25.160 --> 00:17:26.820
Your Highness saved me

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:28.420
And treated me like a human being.

00:17:30.230 --> 00:17:31.140
From then on,

00:17:32.100 --> 00:17:34.900
My life belongs to Your Highness.

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:39.290
My only wish is to repay your kindness.

00:17:40.070 --> 00:17:41.140
I would die without regret.

00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:48.820
Too many have perished already.

00:17:50.640 --> 00:17:51.450
I want you to live.

00:17:52.340 --> 00:17:53.100
From this moment,

00:17:54.200 --> 00:17:55.100
Your life is mine.

00:17:57.550 --> 00:17:58.380
Without my order,

00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:01.050
Never act recklessly again.

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:12.940
Tongzhou,

00:18:13.200 --> 00:18:14.940
Lu and I will rush to join you

00:18:15.200 --> 00:18:16.180
To defeat Zong Quan together.

00:18:23.440 --> 00:18:24.180
Tonghe,

00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:25.770
Uncle,

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:29.380
Now I know my duty.

00:18:30.470 --> 00:18:31.620
I'll never fail you again.

00:18:33.990 --> 00:18:35.690
I shall master the Xuanhua Sacred Fire soon,

00:18:36.270 --> 00:18:37.340
Support Jingwu,

00:18:38.270 --> 00:18:39.490
And guard the Yue State

00:18:40.710 --> 00:18:41.970
For thousands of generations.

00:18:54.160 --> 00:18:54.660
Tongzhou,

00:18:55.840 --> 00:18:56.970
Is your injury flaring up again?

00:18:58.710 --> 00:18:59.290
Stay still.

00:19:20.470 --> 00:19:21.530
I'm breaking through the third level.

00:19:22.470 --> 00:19:23.730
This spirit energy truly works wonders.

00:19:30.550 --> 00:19:31.180
Lifei,

00:19:32.030 --> 00:19:32.660
Are you okay?

00:19:33.710 --> 00:19:34.210
I'm fine.

00:19:35.270 --> 00:19:36.620
How's your injury?

00:19:38.790 --> 00:19:39.450
My bad.

00:19:40.070 --> 00:19:41.660
I made you waste too much spirit energy on me.

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:44.100
No big deal.

00:19:45.270 --> 00:19:46.530
I have the spirit power of Achillea Bead,

00:19:46.550 --> 00:19:47.530
A supreme treasure.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:49.050
It's endless.

00:19:50.200 --> 00:19:50.970
Instead,

00:19:51.340 --> 00:19:53.340
You just healed up. Stay cautious.

00:19:57.880 --> 00:19:59.690
The Dizang Sect won't get involved in Yue's trouble.

00:20:00.070 --> 00:20:01.660
Master locked Ye and me in.

00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:02.900
We can't leave the sect.

00:20:03.440 --> 00:20:04.690
We're trying to escape.

00:20:07.790 --> 00:20:09.490
Can't believe the Longming Sanctuary acts cruelly

00:20:10.340 --> 00:20:11.820
Yet other sects just stand there scared.

00:20:14.070 --> 00:20:15.100
This is always how the immortal sects act.

00:20:15.640 --> 00:20:16.490
To the immortal sects,

00:20:17.400 --> 00:20:19.010
The rise and fall of mortal states

00:20:19.030 --> 00:20:19.820
Are trivial matters.

00:20:20.960 --> 00:20:22.100
They never lift a finger to interfere.

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:24.140
No one helped

00:20:24.680 --> 00:20:25.970
When Gaolu was destroyed.

00:20:26.510 --> 00:20:28.770
They're cold and selfish. It's not surprising.

00:20:29.510 --> 00:20:30.900
Zong Quan practices evil arts and turns evil.

00:20:31.340 --> 00:20:33.900
Why don't all the mountain sect masters stop him?

00:20:35.680 --> 00:20:36.940
Every sect only cares for its own troubles.

00:20:38.510 --> 00:20:39.660
None will step forward.

00:20:40.470 --> 00:20:41.420
We can only rely on ourselves.

00:20:43.070 --> 00:20:45.250
Slaying Zong Quan is my fight.

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:54.050
All of you, leave.

00:20:54.710 --> 00:20:55.770
Don't risk offending the immortal sects for my sake.

00:20:56.550 --> 00:20:58.250
Zong Quan and the Longming Sanctuary are our shared foes.

00:20:58.750 --> 00:21:00.050
We will not stand idly by.

00:21:00.470 --> 00:21:01.730
His cultivation is formidable now.

00:21:02.230 --> 00:21:04.100
The odds are stacked against us. We stand no chance.

00:21:05.030 --> 00:21:06.010
I don't want to drag you down.

00:21:06.750 --> 00:21:08.140
Stop talking nonsense.

00:21:08.470 --> 00:21:09.450
At this critical moment,

00:21:09.710 --> 00:21:11.290
We have to join hands to devise a plan.

00:21:11.920 --> 00:21:12.490
Besides,

00:21:12.790 --> 00:21:14.250
Zong Quan is not who he once was,

00:21:14.270 --> 00:21:15.490
Nor are we.

00:21:15.750 --> 00:21:17.530
If we fight again, we may not lose.

00:21:49.270 --> 00:21:50.580
When you went to worship with Tongzhou,

00:21:51.120 --> 00:21:52.180
Did you drain your spirit power

00:21:52.840 --> 00:21:53.690
To heal his injuries again?

00:21:55.600 --> 00:21:57.380
His deep grief injured his heart meridians.

00:22:01.550 --> 00:22:03.660
I'm fine, just a little tired.

00:22:41.100 --> 00:22:41.690
Xiuyuan.

00:22:49.510 --> 00:22:50.770
If this happens again,

00:22:52.200 --> 00:22:52.940
Let me do it.

00:22:54.840 --> 00:22:56.250
I'm truly alright.

00:22:57.960 --> 00:22:59.530
Strangely enough,

00:23:00.510 --> 00:23:01.900
Ever since we left the White Cliff,

00:23:03.160 --> 00:23:05.340
My spirit power seems to be endless.

00:23:07.550 --> 00:23:08.210
Xiuyuan,

00:23:08.990 --> 00:23:10.140
Is something wrong with me?

00:23:16.600 --> 00:23:17.660
Just cultivation progress.

00:23:18.470 --> 00:23:19.140
Don't overthink it.

00:23:24.160 --> 00:23:25.900
I redrew the Demon-Subduing Formation.

00:23:26.270 --> 00:23:27.690
You know formations well.

00:23:28.070 --> 00:23:28.970
Help me fix its flaws.

00:23:30.470 --> 00:23:31.970
Even if formations are complex,

00:23:32.640 --> 00:23:34.620
If the two parties' strengths fall far behind,

00:23:34.920 --> 00:23:35.660
It won't work.

00:23:36.840 --> 00:23:37.620
Our top priority

00:23:38.200 --> 00:23:39.620
Is to ambush Zong Quan

00:23:40.470 --> 00:23:41.140
While he's injured.

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:42.450
Is he injured?

00:23:43.400 --> 00:23:44.860
He didn't appear when Lanya

00:23:45.550 --> 00:23:46.490
Tried to trap us.

00:23:47.160 --> 00:23:50.290
It must be his cultivation deviation.

00:23:52.440 --> 00:23:53.420
Fell into demonic possession?

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:55.860
That's not right.

00:23:56.750 --> 00:23:58.420
He always practices demonic arts.

00:23:59.230 --> 00:24:00.340
Every art has weaknesses,

00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:01.530
And everyone's

00:24:01.880 --> 00:24:03.290
Spirit power differs.

00:24:03.790 --> 00:24:05.690
Zong Quan steals others' power

00:24:06.470 --> 00:24:07.250
And needs to refine it.

00:24:07.990 --> 00:24:08.530
I think

00:24:09.070 --> 00:24:11.100
Elder Xuanshan released Burning Flame power

00:24:11.340 --> 00:24:12.340
Before he died,

00:24:12.680 --> 00:24:13.620
Which backfired on Zong Quan.

00:24:14.990 --> 00:24:15.690
Xiuyuan,

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:18.420
How do you know so much?

00:24:19.270 --> 00:24:21.820
I read more books than you.

00:24:46.160 --> 00:24:48.010
The Spirit-Devouring Canon is from the Primordial Era.

00:24:48.310 --> 00:24:50.860
You can't master it in a short time.

00:24:51.710 --> 00:24:53.250
You just destroyed Xingzheng Hall

00:24:53.440 --> 00:24:55.340
And absorbed many cultivators' power.

00:24:55.680 --> 00:24:56.770
Don't push too hard.

00:24:57.230 --> 00:24:59.210
My chest has ached recently.

00:25:00.470 --> 00:25:05.340
Is Rakshasa's life talisman acting up?

00:25:05.790 --> 00:25:06.490
Let me check.

00:25:12.550 --> 00:25:15.210
Zong Quan, you're asking for death!

00:25:26.200 --> 00:25:27.420
You refined the Burning Flame!

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:32.900
With Xuanshanzi's Burning Flame

00:25:33.030 --> 00:25:34.530
And the Spirit-Devouring Demonic Arts,

00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:37.210
I'll become immortal soon.

00:25:37.600 --> 00:25:39.970
I won't be the demon clan's

00:25:39.990 --> 00:25:41.050
Puppet anymore.

00:25:50.510 --> 00:25:51.660
The Guardian used Zong Quan

00:25:51.920 --> 00:25:52.860
To divide the immortal sects,

00:25:53.340 --> 00:25:55.010
But he broke free from the life talisman

00:25:55.270 --> 00:25:56.180
And became a huge threat.

00:25:57.600 --> 00:25:59.770
Does he have any weak points?

00:26:00.470 --> 00:26:01.010
Uh...

00:26:01.960 --> 00:26:02.380
Answer me!

00:26:02.640 --> 00:26:03.530
I don't know.

00:26:03.880 --> 00:26:05.530
But Demon Lord Yecha's supreme power

00:26:05.750 --> 00:26:07.970
Can cut his spirit root and kill immortals.

00:26:10.550 --> 00:26:11.530
Go warn Rakshasa

00:26:11.990 --> 00:26:12.820
To watch her step.

00:26:24.920 --> 00:26:25.250
Hurry.

00:26:27.750 --> 00:26:28.140
Capture him!

00:26:33.470 --> 00:26:34.580
Zhao Mingli?

00:26:35.960 --> 00:26:36.970
It's you.

00:26:37.400 --> 00:26:39.660
Lanya, you killed Zhijie

00:26:39.920 --> 00:26:41.010
And His Highness.

00:26:41.340 --> 00:26:42.530
I'm going to avenge them.

00:26:42.790 --> 00:26:44.940
What's wrong with Tongzhou?

00:26:45.340 --> 00:26:46.770
His Highness's injuries were fatal.

00:26:47.750 --> 00:26:48.420
He's...

00:26:49.440 --> 00:26:50.380
He's dead.

00:26:51.680 --> 00:26:52.340
That's a lie!

00:26:52.640 --> 00:26:53.860
He would never die.

00:26:54.070 --> 00:26:55.530
I wish it weren't true.

00:26:56.070 --> 00:26:58.690
Zhijie and His Highness are both gone.

00:26:58.990 --> 00:27:00.820
Is this what you wanted, Lanya?

00:27:01.640 --> 00:27:02.210
Where's

00:27:03.100 --> 00:27:04.250
Tongzhou's body?

00:27:04.640 --> 00:27:07.180
At the Orchid Pavilion, north of the city.

00:27:09.990 --> 00:27:10.660
Orchid Pavilion.

00:27:12.150 --> 00:27:17.800
[Orchid Pavilion]

00:27:22.230 --> 00:27:23.730
Tongzhou. Tongzhou.

00:27:24.400 --> 00:27:25.620
I knew you weren't dead.

00:27:26.200 --> 00:27:26.730
Tongzhou,

00:27:27.200 --> 00:27:28.660
Don't hate me.

00:27:29.270 --> 00:27:30.770
I never wanted to hurt you. Really.

00:27:32.270 --> 00:27:33.970
Zong Quan made me do it.

00:27:38.200 --> 00:27:38.860
Tongzhou.

00:27:43.160 --> 00:27:44.380
What did they make you do?

00:27:53.070 --> 00:27:54.450
Zong Quan took me captive

00:27:55.510 --> 00:27:57.250
When my parents died for the country.

00:27:57.600 --> 00:27:59.660
He put a Gu seal on me

00:28:02.550 --> 00:28:04.490
Before we reached Duantu to control me,

00:28:05.470 --> 00:28:07.100
So I have to follow his orders.

00:28:13.710 --> 00:28:14.580
Is this Longming Seal?

00:28:18.070 --> 00:28:19.770
It tortures me with worm pain

00:28:20.550 --> 00:28:22.290
Whenever I disobey him.

00:28:23.470 --> 00:28:24.530
It's unbearable.

00:28:27.840 --> 00:28:28.380
Tongzhou,

00:28:30.070 --> 00:28:31.940
I never wanted to hurt Tonghe

00:28:32.200 --> 00:28:33.940
Or Mr. Xuanshan.

00:28:34.470 --> 00:28:37.180
But if I refused Zong Quan,

00:28:37.600 --> 00:28:38.860
He'd kill you.

00:28:39.710 --> 00:28:40.210
Tongzhou,

00:28:40.710 --> 00:28:42.660
I only acted to protect you.

00:28:43.120 --> 00:28:44.770
My feelings for you never changed.

00:28:45.160 --> 00:28:46.450
I swear. I never lied.

00:28:46.470 --> 00:28:47.660
Trust me.

00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:53.690
Tongzhou.

00:28:56.990 --> 00:28:59.770
If you really want to help me,

00:29:02.120 --> 00:29:03.290
Kill Zong Quan.

00:29:11.640 --> 00:29:12.340
Tongzhou,

00:29:16.750 --> 00:29:17.770
Do you hate me?

00:29:24.400 --> 00:29:25.530
I'd be lying if I said no.

00:29:26.310 --> 00:29:27.690
You killed my uncle

00:29:28.230 --> 00:29:29.050
And betrayed me.

00:29:33.790 --> 00:29:34.380
But

00:29:35.840 --> 00:29:37.690
I've always regarded you as my family.

00:29:38.680 --> 00:29:40.490
Right now, I can rely only on you.

00:29:41.120 --> 00:29:41.660
Lanya,

00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:44.290
Kill Zong Quan,

00:29:45.750 --> 00:29:47.660
And we'll forget everything that happened before.

00:29:52.200 --> 00:29:53.210
What about Jiang Lifei?

00:29:56.070 --> 00:29:57.180
Won't she help you?

00:30:03.680 --> 00:30:05.250
She only cares about Lei Xiuyuan.

00:30:06.790 --> 00:30:08.530
Gelin and the others

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:12.010
Are too weak to help much anyway.

00:30:21.270 --> 00:30:21.770
Help me,

00:30:22.960 --> 00:30:23.620
Lanya.

00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:26.420
After I kill Zong Quan

00:30:27.470 --> 00:30:28.490
And become emperor,

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:31.250
You'll be my empress.

00:30:36.470 --> 00:30:37.420
Then nobody

00:30:38.230 --> 00:30:39.580
Can threaten you anymore.

00:30:40.440 --> 00:30:43.490
We'll work together to rebuild the Yue State.

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:58.580
How can I prove I'm sincere?

00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:15.010
This is a Heartbound Gu.

00:31:15.880 --> 00:31:16.730
Take it,

00:31:18.440 --> 00:31:19.820
And we'll live or die together.

00:31:32.680 --> 00:31:33.380
Tongzhou.

00:31:54.990 --> 00:31:55.820
Keep Jingwu safe.

00:31:56.200 --> 00:31:57.940
If you hear nothing by Chen hour,

00:31:58.200 --> 00:31:59.180
Leave Duantu right away.

00:31:59.790 --> 00:32:02.010
Go to Fengchu Academy for Mr. Zuo Qiu.

00:32:04.750 --> 00:32:05.450
Don't worry, Your Highness.

00:32:06.030 --> 00:32:07.730
I'll finish what you asked,

00:32:08.120 --> 00:32:08.820
No matter the cost.

00:32:10.310 --> 00:32:12.340
Uncle, focus on your mission.

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:14.290
I've grown up,

00:32:14.310 --> 00:32:15.690
And I can take care of myself.

00:32:20.510 --> 00:32:21.420
Be a good boy.

00:32:25.270 --> 00:32:25.820
Go now.

00:32:26.880 --> 00:32:28.050
Your Royal Highness, let's go.

00:32:54.230 --> 00:32:54.770
Understood.

00:32:58.120 --> 00:32:59.140
What's wrong, Your Ladyship?

00:32:59.510 --> 00:33:00.860
Drinking to forget your pain?

00:33:03.310 --> 00:33:04.660
Tongzhou must hate me.

00:33:05.750 --> 00:33:09.490
I have no one left in this world.

00:33:10.710 --> 00:33:12.250
My life is meaningless.

00:33:15.360 --> 00:33:16.970
Tongzhou is gone,

00:33:17.750 --> 00:33:19.250
But I'm still here for you.

00:33:23.030 --> 00:33:23.860
Senior Brother.

00:33:48.550 --> 00:33:49.620
I knew you were plotting something.

00:33:50.550 --> 00:33:51.770
You're useless now.

00:33:52.510 --> 00:33:53.530
Meet your end.

00:33:58.710 --> 00:33:59.340
Lu Li?

00:34:00.960 --> 00:34:01.860
Gelin sent me to help you.

00:34:02.440 --> 00:34:03.860
Another fool begging to die.

00:34:04.510 --> 00:34:06.900
Fine, I'll send you both off.

00:34:25.840 --> 00:34:26.860
What's this?

00:34:27.220 --> 00:34:28.610
Instant-kill poison.

00:34:29.110 --> 00:34:29.900
You're getting off easy.

00:34:39.920 --> 00:34:41.900
Father, he is ahead.

00:34:42.280 --> 00:34:43.450
Must be the doing of Jiang Lifei's group.

00:35:31.470 --> 00:35:33.220
Fighting back desperately?

00:35:33.510 --> 00:35:35.420
I'll finish you off!

00:35:43.220 --> 00:35:44.610
The Sea Sect's Evasive Talisman Technique.

00:36:02.590 --> 00:36:04.340
You're way better now.

00:36:30.590 --> 00:36:31.860
Yecha's supreme power

00:36:32.220 --> 00:36:34.420
Can cut his spirit root and kill immortals.

00:36:40.760 --> 00:36:41.420
Demon.

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:09.420
The Divine Tree's spirit aura.

00:37:10.670 --> 00:37:12.220
You're the Divine Tree!

00:37:48.550 --> 00:37:49.970
You're the Divine Tree!

00:37:57.150 --> 00:37:57.820
Master,

00:37:58.190 --> 00:38:00.820
Why do those spirits keep pestering me?

00:38:01.110 --> 00:38:01.900
Because

00:38:02.320 --> 00:38:04.490
They love your sweet scent.

00:38:04.990 --> 00:38:05.820
Sweet scent?

00:38:22.590 --> 00:38:23.450
Five centuries ago,

00:38:23.700 --> 00:38:26.450
Demon Lord Yecha was obsessed with the Divine Tree.

00:38:26.990 --> 00:38:29.130
Couldn't have it, so he tried to destroy it.

00:38:43.070 --> 00:38:44.260
According to the surviving guards,

00:38:44.840 --> 00:38:46.530
Zong Quan threw captured Xingzheng Hall disciples here

00:38:46.990 --> 00:38:48.010
To absorb their power.

00:38:49.150 --> 00:38:50.820
All were thrown in alive.

00:38:51.510 --> 00:38:53.700
Their broken souls fill this place with rage.

00:38:54.670 --> 00:38:56.300
Plus Zong Quan's demonic spirit,

00:38:56.920 --> 00:38:59.570
This altar became a soul-slaughtering purgatory.

00:39:00.670 --> 00:39:01.970
Ordinary people can't get close.

00:39:02.990 --> 00:39:04.170
I don't know what to do.

00:39:04.990 --> 00:39:06.940
Lei Xiuyuan, you're stronger.

00:39:07.670 --> 00:39:08.820
Can you purify this place?

00:39:16.190 --> 00:39:16.820
Don't come closer.

00:39:18.920 --> 00:39:19.940
The demonic energy may corrupt you.

00:39:21.880 --> 00:39:22.700
I'll take care of it.

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:24.050
Go handle other things.

00:39:25.800 --> 00:39:26.650
I'll count on you.

00:39:50.400 --> 00:39:51.170
Lifei,

00:39:52.150 --> 00:39:53.420
You should rest in your room.

00:39:54.460 --> 00:39:55.170
Feeling better?

00:39:57.070 --> 00:39:57.780
Yes, I'm okay.

00:40:02.760 --> 00:40:05.530
Can they never reincarnate?

00:40:06.590 --> 00:40:07.380
Hatred lingers after death.

00:40:08.470 --> 00:40:09.530
Their souls

00:40:11.110 --> 00:40:11.970
Won't let go.

00:40:12.670 --> 00:40:14.490
I have to block it with a formation

00:40:15.190 --> 00:40:16.530
To keep ordinary people safe.

00:40:17.900 --> 00:40:18.860
They'll be trapped here forever

00:40:19.860 --> 00:40:20.780
With no way out.

00:40:22.300 --> 00:40:23.530
How tragic for them.

00:40:27.670 --> 00:40:28.780
Let's go to Tongzhou.

00:40:29.510 --> 00:40:31.860
The Xuanhua Sacred Fire might clear their hatred.

00:40:40.380 --> 00:40:41.340
If they can be cleared

00:40:42.820 --> 00:40:43.700
And start over,

00:40:44.900 --> 00:40:46.010
That'll be the best result.

00:41:36.990 --> 00:41:37.530
Jingwu,

00:41:38.190 --> 00:41:39.900
After your coronation three days later,

00:41:40.340 --> 00:41:41.530
You'll be the emperor

00:41:42.340 --> 00:41:44.530
And carry the Yue State on your shoulders.

00:41:45.470 --> 00:41:48.010
I'm too young and unlearned.

00:41:48.030 --> 00:41:50.050
You should be the emperor.

00:41:54.980 --> 00:41:56.050
I've joined the immortal sect

00:41:56.720 --> 00:41:59.610
And will be Xingzheng Hall's Immortal Lord soon.

00:42:00.470 --> 00:42:01.170
Don't worry.

00:42:01.670 --> 00:42:03.300
I'll always back you up,

00:42:03.990 --> 00:42:04.740
Just like

00:42:07.300 --> 00:42:09.970
My uncle supported your father.

00:42:10.920 --> 00:42:12.610
How dare you stop me!

00:42:13.280 --> 00:42:14.130
How dare you!

00:42:15.070 --> 00:42:16.010
Sorry, Your Ladyship.

00:42:16.400 --> 00:42:17.300
His Majesty forbids

00:42:17.590 --> 00:42:18.780
Anyone from entering.

00:42:19.380 --> 00:42:20.130
You?

00:42:22.510 --> 00:42:26.450
You're the maid who took Jingwu away!

00:42:29.190 --> 00:42:31.260
I'm Miaoqing. Greetings, Your Ladyship.

00:42:33.980 --> 00:42:36.900
Insulting nobility is punishable by death.

00:42:37.940 --> 00:42:38.900
Drag her off and flog her to death.

00:42:38.940 --> 00:42:39.340
- Yes. - Yes.

00:42:39.360 --> 00:42:39.900
Wait!

00:42:42.050 --> 00:42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:42.360 --> 00:42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:55.800 --> 00:42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

00:42:59.800 --> 00:43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:43:02.560 --> 00:43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

00:43:05.800 --> 00:43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

00:43:09.200 --> 00:43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

00:43:13.360 --> 00:43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

00:43:23.080 --> 00:43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:43:27.480 --> 00:43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:43:30.360 --> 00:43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:43:32.400 --> 00:43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:43:36.880 --> 00:43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:43:41.080 --> 00:43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:43:44.160 --> 00:43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:43:50.480 --> 00:43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

00:44:11.400 --> 00:44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:44:14.280 --> 00:44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

00:44:17.680 --> 00:44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

00:44:21.160 --> 00:44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

00:44:25.160 --> 00:44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

00:44:28.600 --> 00:44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

00:44:35.000 --> 00:44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:44:39.200 --> 00:44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:44:42.160 --> 00:44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:44:44.160 --> 00:44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:44:48.600 --> 00:44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:44:52.720 --> 00:44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:44:55.960 --> 00:45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:45:02.720 --> 00:45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

00:45:06.920 --> 00:45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

00:45:09.800 --> 00:45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

00:45:11.880 --> 00:45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

00:45:16.360 --> 00:45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

00:45:20.440 --> 00:45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

00:45:23.600 --> 00:45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

00:45:30.000 --> 00:45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

